  sibling openexam-demo-library repo via `<import>` and adds two
  inline questions of its own. Section headings like "Part 1" /
  "Part 2" stay in the rendered exam; the per-question dev annotations
  ("multipleChoice (no sugar)", "matchPairs canonical form", …) live
  in HTML comments so they don't leak to the student.
-->
